summary: This document consists of an email chain discussing a subpoena and related materials. The correspondence indicates that the sender and recipients are coordinating on the handling of the subpoena and the necessary documentation. The emails emphasize confidentiality regarding the subpoena's existence.
keyFacts: The email chain discusses a subpoena and the handling of related materials.
The sender requests that materials be printed and ready for pickup on July 14th.
Recipients are instructed not to discuss the existence of the subpoena with third parties.
There are multiple references to email correspondence regarding the title order and due diligence timeline.
The email emphasizes the confidentiality of the information contained within.
